I"{<p>In videography, B-rolls are short clips inserted during narration. They temporarily nudge viewers into a state of <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/metabolism-influences-neural-dynamics">diffused attention</a>, helping them cycle through different <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/dreaming-exploits-idiosyncratic-neural-dynamics">levels of focus</a>.</p>
